1998;;My Dog Vincent;;Canadian;;Michael McGowan;;Chuck Campbell, Zehra Leverman;;coming-of-age drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/My_Dog_Vincent;;The film is centered on O'Brien (played by Chuck Campbell) and his friends, Wiley and Harper. These three twenty-something young men still live at home, and are looking to expand their horizons in life and love. This coming-of-age story is weaved with their hobbies and interests, both existing and new, one of which is an obsession with Vincent Price.